
---

# 🧹 2️⃣ .gitignore (VERY IMPORTANT)

Create a file named **`.gitignore`** in the **root folder**.

### ✅ COPY–PASTE THIS

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/

# Environment files
.env

# Uploads (videos)
backend/uploads/

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Build folders
dist/
build/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Vite cache
.vite/

# Editor folders
.vscode/
.idea/
